title: JUN 23, 2022 - BIDEN FBI RAIDS GOP OFFICIALS IN MULTIPLE STATES IN ‘ALTERNATE ELECTORS’ PROBE
description:
BREAKING: The Biden Department of Justice is sending FBI agents to raid GOP officials in multiple states with the purpose of investigating ‘alternate electors’ related to the 2020 election. Huge win for the second amendment: the Supreme Court has struck down the New York State law imposing concealed carry restrictions. The Uvalde School Police Chief, Arredondo, is placed on administrative leave. And finally, conservatives are demanding that DHS designate members of Jane’s Revenge as domestic terrorists.
